        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3261504757" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11986482181214798855">This was a fun book in many ways, but is best suited for someone who enjoys all things nautical, which I am not. I still liked it, I just got tired of all the crazy theories on how to figure out longitude. <br/><br/>It was interesting to read at this time, though. This guy was truly isolated, alone on a ship. We have so many ways to still reach people but he had only his imagination. He made excellent use of it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


